data.description: Seller will contribute $5,000 to buyers closing costs!!! MOVE-IN READY HOME IN FORNEY! This home combines style, comfort, and functionality! With its open concept floorplan and oversize windows, natural light floods throughout, creating an inviting atmosphere. The heart of this home is the living area, with a cozy fireplace perfect for chilly evenings. Mornings on the go are a breeze with the breakfast bar, and the kitchen is accommodating for the serious chef. Relax in the spacious ensuite master, complete with a walk-in closet. Then step outside onto the covered back porch and to enjoy your morning coffee or host a summer BBQ. Imagine coming home each day to your new home filled with modern convenience and cozy comfort – a true haven you'll be proud to call your own. Located in an INNOVATIVE COMMUNITY, walking distance to park, pool, & schools. Convenient 30-minute commute straight into Dallas. Enjoy easy access to Rockwall and Dallas shopping, restaurants, and retail.
